title: 1966 Presidential Cup
text: 1966 Presidential Cup was the inaugural edition of the national super cup of Turkish Football Federation. The match was contested between <a href="1965%E2%80%9366%201.Lig">1965–66 1.Lig</a> champions <a href="Be%C5%9Fikta%C5%9F%20J.K.">Beşiktaş</a> and <a href="1965%E2%80%9366%20Turkish%20Cup">1965–66 Turkish Cup</a> winners <a href="Galatasaray%20S.K.%20%28football%20team%29">Galatasaray</a>. It was held on an unusual time for a <a href="super%20cup">super cup</a>, in September, after the footballing season for <a href="1966%E2%80%9367%201.Lig">1966–67 1.Lig</a> began.
